msgid "Country Blocker"
msgstr "Bacadh Dùthaich"

msgid "Settings saved."
msgstr "Roghainnean air an sàbhaladh."

msgid "Unknown"
msgstr "Neo-aithnichte"

msgid "Enable country blocking"
msgstr "Cuir bacadh Dùthaich an gnìomh."

msgid "Enable IP-based country blocking"
msgstr "Cuir bacadh Dùthaich stèidhichte air IP an gnìomh."

msgid "This plugin works only when IP-based blocking is enabled."
msgstr ""
"Tha am plug-in seo ag obair dìreach ma tha bacadh stèidhichte air IP air a "
"chur an gnìomh."

msgid ""
"Enable IP-based country blocking (uses ip-api.com | 45 requests per minute |"
" Free Version)"
msgstr ""
"Cuir bacadh Dùthaich stèidhichte air IP an gnìomh (a’ cleachdadh ip-api.com "
"| 45 iarrtasan gach mionaid | Leagan an-asgaidh)"

msgid "Save settings"
msgstr "Sàbhail na roghainnean."

msgid "Dismiss"
msgstr "Cuir às."

msgid "Valeri"
msgstr "Valeri"

msgid "Hi, I'm Valeri 👋"
msgstr "Halò, mise Valeri 👋"

msgid "Thanks for using this plugin."
msgstr "Tapadh leat airson cleachdadh an plugin seo."

msgid ""
"If you are looking for more helpful plugins, you can check out my website."
msgstr ""
"Ma tha thu a’ lorg barrachd plugins cuideachail, faodaidh tu mo làrach-lìn a"
" sheiceáil."

msgid "If you like this plugin, I would be happy about a review."
msgstr ""
"Ma tha thu a’ còrdadh ris an plugin seo, bu mhath leam lèirmheas fhaighinn."

msgid "premium-plugin.com"
msgstr "premium-plugin.com"

msgid "Rate this plugin"
msgstr "Dèan meas air an plugin seo."

msgid "Your detected country:"
msgstr "Dùthaich a tha thu air aithneachadh:"

msgid "Block all except my country"
msgstr "Cùm bacadh air a h-uile càil ach mo dhùthaich."

msgid "Unblock all"
msgstr "fosgail gach bacadh."

msgid "Country"
msgstr "Dùthaich"

msgid "Status"
msgstr "Staid"

msgid "Block"
msgstr "Bac"

msgid "Blocked"
msgstr "Air bac"

msgid "Allowed"
msgstr "Ceadaichte"

#. translators: %s is the visitor's country code, e.g. 'DE' or 'US'
msgid "Access from your country (%s) has been blocked."
msgstr "Tha rochtain bhon dhùthaich agad (%s) air a bacadh."
